   "git is the storage backend only — query sys_command_alt for jj equivalents",
   "global", "manifest", "eternal"],
  ["push-to-main", "vcs", "mars",
   "Push means push to main — no feature branches",
   "single-branch workflow — describe, new, bookmark set main, git push",
   "global", "manifest", "proven"],
  ["commit-message-tuples", "vcs", "saturn",
   "Commit messages are CozoScript tuple-of-three-tuples (Sol/Luna/Saturnus)",
